---
layout: base.njk
title: "O Método ChefBrico | Comida de Verdade em 18 Minutos"
permalink: /comida-de-verdade/
---

<style>
    /* 1. SEÇÃO HERO - MARIA CONCEIÇÃO (E-E-A-T) */
    .metodo-hero {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 50px;
        padding: 60px 24px;
        max-width: 1100px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .avatar-wrapper {
        width: 240px;
        height: 240px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        border: 8px solid #FDFBF7;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        overflow: hidden;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .avatar-wrapper img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }

    @media (max-width: 992px) {
        .metodo-hero { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; padding: 40px 24px; }
        .avatar-wrapper { width: 180px; height: 180px; }
    }

    /* 2. CARROSSEL DE PILARES (PADRÃO APPLE 16:10) */
    .pilares-carousel {
        display: flex;
        overflow-x: auto;
        gap: 20px;
        padding: 20px 24px 60px;
        scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
        scrollbar-width: none;
    }
    .pilares-carousel::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }

    .pilar-card {
        flex: 0 0 300px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
        backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
        border-radius: 20px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        overflow: hidden;
        scroll-snap-align: start;
    }
    .moldura-pilar {
        width: 100%;
        aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
        overflow: hidden;
    }
    .moldura-pilar img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .pilar-card { flex: 0 0 260px; }
    }

    /* 3. GRID DE SABORES (A REGRA REAL: 3 MOBILE / 6 DESKTOP) */
    .metodo-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); /* TRAVA 3 COLUNAS MOBILE */
        gap: 12px;
        padding: 0 24px 120px;
        max-width: 1300px;
        margin: 50px auto 0;
    }

    @media (min-width: 1024px) {
        .metodo-grid {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr); /* TRAVA 6 COLUNAS DESKTOP */
            gap: 25px;
        }
    }

    /* CARD DE RECEITA INDIVIDUAL */
    .recipe-card-mini {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 16px;
        overflow: hidden;
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    .moldura-1-1 { width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 1 / 1; overflow: hidden; }
    .moldura-1-1 img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }

    .btn-add-metodo {
        position: absolute;
        top: 8px; right: 8px;
        width: 30px; height: 30px;
        background: #F2811D;
        color: white;
        border: 2px solid white;
        border-radius: 50%;
        font-weight: bold;
        display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
        cursor: pointer; z-index: 10;
    }

    .recipe-info-mini { padding: 10px 5px; text-align: center; }
    .recipe-info-mini h4 { 
        font-size: 0.65rem; color: #014039; margin: 0; 
        line-height: 1.2; height: 2.4em; overflow: hidden;
        display: -webkit-box; -webkit-line-clamp: 2; -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
    }
</style>

<section class="metodo-hero">
    <div class="avatar-wrapper">
        <img src="/img/maria-conceicao.jpg" alt="Maria Conceição - ChefBrico">
    </div>
    <div class="hero-content">
        <h1 style="font-family: 'Merriweather', serif; color: #014039; font-size: 2.5rem;">O Método</h1>
        <p style="color: #666; font-size: 1.1rem; max-width: 500px;">Comida de verdade, ultracongelada a vácuo, preservando 100% dos nutrientes para sua saúde.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<div class="pilares-carousel">
    <div class="pilar-card">
        <div class="moldura-pilar"><img src="/img/pilar-vacuo.jpg" alt="Vácuo"></div>
        <div style="padding: 15px;"><h3 style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #014039;">Tecnologia a Vácuo</h3></div>
    </div>
    <div class="pilar-card">
        <div class="moldura-pilar"><img src="/img/pilar-nutricao.jpg" alt="Nutrição"></div>
        <div style="padding: 15px;"><h3 style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #014039;">Nutrição Preservada</h3></div>
    </div>
    <div class="pilar-card">
        <div class="moldura-pilar"><img src="/img/pilar-sabor.jpg" alt="Sabor"></div>
        <div style="padding: 15px;"><h3 style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #014039;">Sabor de Chef</h3></div>
    </div>
</div>

<h2 style="text-align: center; color: #014039; margin-top: 60px;">Escolha por este Método:</h2>
<div class="metodo-grid">
    {% for item in collections.receitas %}
    {% if item.data.price %}
    <div class="recipe-card-mini">
        <button class="btn-add-metodo" 
                onclick="addToGame('{{ item.data.title }}', {{ item.data.price }}, '{{ item.data.image }}', '{{ item.data.sku }}')">
            +
        </button>
        <a href="{{ item.url }}" class="moldura-1-1">
            <img src="{{ item.data.image }}" alt="{{ item.data.title }}" loading="lazy">
        </a>
        <div class="recipe-info-mini">
            <h4>{{ item.data.title | replace(" | ChefBrico", "") }}</h4>
            <span style="color: #25D366; font-weight: 800; font-size: 0.8rem;">R$ {{ item.data.price | dinheiro }}</span>
        </div>
    </div>
    {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
</div>
